levelinfo:
Far from the lands of war, 
death and suffering an old forest stands,
energetic and wise. Spreading vastly 
over miles of land, 
	It is no ordinary place.
Blessed by the god of nature, trees tower 
over a 100 meters above the rich 
and lush forest including a variety of 
wild and plantlife.
objectives: Claim shrines to win extra timesync points.
